  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel National is on a half board basis. A fruit basket is provided on arrival.</p>
<p>Fuel up for the day at the breakfast buffet, where you have a continental offering including bread, pastries, meats and cheese, as well as additional hot options including eggs prepared to order. Served daily between 7-10.30am. </p>
<p>When you have returned from a day of exploring Zermatt, enjoy complimentary afternoon tea with tea and cake. </p>
<p>Each evening you will be treated to a four course evening meal inspired by Swiss cuisine served in the Restaurant National. The menu is prepared using local and seasonal produce, and includes<span> Valais specialities, traditional Swiss meals and menus - </span>you will have a choice of main dish including cheese fondue. The adjoining <span>Stübli a la carte restaurant is also open to hotel guests, serving a range of Swiss specialities. </span></p>
<p>Children’s menus are available from 5pm.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala meal included</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
