  <description><![CDATA[<p>Set in a quiet location, opposite the Sunnegga Lift the staff at this hotel has a genuine interest in your wellbeing and enjoyment during your stay. The management and staff ensure your memories last for all the right reasons. The bar area contains a warm wood-burning fireplace, which is a nice place to unwind before dinner and has ample space to play board games. The recently renovated spa area and wellness centre is a wonderful oasis of calm and tranquillity ideally placed for a rest after a day on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Excellent location</h2>
<p>Located opposite the Sunnegga lift, the Hotel National has an enviable location in Zermatt. Keen skiers and snowboarders can start their day with ease, as the lift is less than 50 metres from the hotel, taking you up onto the fantastic slopes of <a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> - and when you return for the day, there is a heated boot room where you can store your equipment. If you want to venture out, the resort centre is a short walk away where you can find a range of bars, cafes and restaurants, and souvenir shops selling trinkets so you can remember your <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Swiss</a> trip.</p>
<h2>Lounge with fireplace</h2>
<p>Warm up in front of the fire with a complimentary sweet treat and cup of coffee or enjoy a hand-crafted cocktail with friends and family after dinner. There is also a unsupervised kids corner with toys and a television. When the weather is nicer the terrace is open, and it is a great spot to marvel at the mountain and make the most of the winter sunshine.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of skiing, snowboarding or hiking, the spa and wellness centre is the perfect spot to unwind and relax. Take a dip in the pool, <span>and then head to the adults only spa area to unwind the jacuzzi or relax in the sauna or fragrant steam bath. There is also a range of treatments and massages available to book for a moment of pure relaxation. If you still have energy to burn, there is also a fitness room with a range of machines and weights.</span></p>]]></description>
